https://github.com/radar/guides/blob/master/gem-development.md

Requires rubygems and the following gems: json, shoulda

Using Ubuntu / Debian apt-get:
sudo apt-get install rubygems
sudo gem install json shoulda

Using Windows / OS X:
# Download rubygems from: http://rubygems.org/pages/download
#   Install:
ruby setup.rb # In rubygems directory
gem install json shoulda
